  "signal_description": "This SIGNAL query retrieves the number of cases, the average cycle time, and the purchasing group from the 'defaultview-124' table. It groups the results by the 'Purchasing Group' column and orders them in descending order based on the number of cases. The query also limits the output to 50 rows. The 'No. of Cases' column represents the count of 'CASE_ID' values. The 'Avg. Cycle Time' column is calculated by subtracting the last 'END_TIME' value where the 'EVENT_NAME' is 'Create Goods Receipt' from the last 'END_TIME' value where the 'EVENT_NAME' is 'Receive Advanced Shipment Notice (ASN)'. The 'Purchasing Group' column displays the values from the 'PO Purchasing Group Text' column."
